eminder of the vastness of the deep ocean.","is_correct":true,"explanation":"Choice D matches the question''s requirement and is consistent with the passage''s central claim or supporting detail. Re-read the sentences surrounding the key detail before eliminating this option on test day."}]'::jsonb,
